727618f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - Parsons Boulevard
727618f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, no: th side, east from Parsons Boule-
vard to 146th Street. The first house, now abandoned, is the
J. Bramwell house of 1891. The site is being offered for sale.
The bther homes are of modern design.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
